metadata.name: Dusty Pubes #1
metadata.description: This is a collection of 2500 pubes immersed in dusts of different colors and gestures, psst! Legend says this collection contains pubes of all species and even ALIENS, have fun choosing the pubes that best describes you. Guess what, there will be more and you don't want to miss it so join the pubic town discord and follow the pubes twitter account. IMPORTANT: In order to get whitelisted join our discord and follow our twitter, the rest will be done on discord this opportunity is only for the first 100 people to join. This Collection will be available for minting in a few days so if you are interested join and follow. You will find the minting link there.
